high_descs: Turn to the left, walk forward to the window and turn to the left again.
Pick up the knife in front of the lettuce.
Turn to face the opposite direction and walk to the front of the sink.
Slice the apple in the sink with the knife.
Place the knife into the sink.
Pick up the sliced apple from the sink.
Turn to the left twice and face the front of the stove.
Place the apple slice into the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Turn to the left and proceed to the table to the right of the door and face it.
Place the pot on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple for the pot on the stove and put the pot on the counter to the right of the door.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to face the right side of the sink.
Cut the apple in the right side of the sink.
Place the knife in the right side of the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple from in the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the stove.
Place the piece of apple in the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan with the piece of apple in it.
Turn left and walk across the room and turn right to face the table on the right.
Place the pan with the piece of apple in it on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To place a pan with a piece of apple in it and place it on the white table.
